PROJECT BLAZE - EXPLICIT LONG INPUT TEST DATA
=============================================

Purpose
-------
This file documents a long demo workload for the Project Blaze robot scheduler.
It is written to match the backend demo dataset and the frontend scheduling
comparison panel.

Assumptions used by this input
------------------------------
1. Worker / robot count: 3
2. Scheduling strategies compared: FIFO and Priority
3. All tasks are seeded into the scheduler at demo time t = 0 s
4. Priority strategy is non-preemptive:
	- High > Normal > Low
	- FIFO order is preserved inside the same priority level
5. Task duration is the simulated execution duration


